    govEffectiveness: "41st percentile reflects bureaucratic complexity, inconsistent policy implementation across 26 states plus federal district, and infrastructure gaps. Brazil has functional institutions but they are often slow and unevenly effective. Digital government services have improved significantly in recent years.",
