    govEffectiveness: "70th percentile reflects a highly capable bureaucratic apparatus in economic management, infrastructure delivery, and crisis response. The one-party system enables rapid policy implementation. Critics argue this metric does not capture the costs of top-down decision-making, including policy errors that lack corrective feedback mechanisms.",
