    govEffectiveness: "90th percentile reflects professional bureaucracy, strong rule-based governance, and effective federal system. Germany's institutions are designed for consensus and stability. Administrative processes can be slow by design — thoroughness is valued over speed. Digital government services lag behind peers.",
