    voiceAccountability: "95th percentile reflects robust democracy, independent and diverse media (strong public broadcasters ARD/ZDF), active civil society, and constitutional protections (Basic Law). Historical experience with totalitarianism has produced strong institutional safeguards. Some concerns about hate speech enforcement balancing free expression.",
