    voiceAccountability: "62nd percentile reflects one of Africa's most stable democracies, with regular peaceful transfers of power since 1992, an active and diverse media landscape, and constitutional protections for expression. Some concerns about media polarisation along party lines and occasional harassment of journalists.",
