    gpi: "Score of 2.55 reflects multiple security challenges: ongoing tensions with Pakistan and China, internal insurgencies in several regions (Naxalite/Maoist, northeastern states), communal violence incidents, and significant military spending (5th largest globally). No large-scale active war but persistent localised conflicts.",
